{"tid":1744510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[忽發奇想] 有冇聽過非牛頓流體？呢種液體愈大力打佢，佢就愈硬。","createTime":"2019-11-21T18:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T13:19:32.000Z","uid":203476,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7f78700d0bb853f0011679e73408653c797fc4","tid":1744510,"uid":203476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T18:45:04.000Z","msg":"話說頭先做緊Chem功課，之前做實驗用過鷹粟粉，頭先上Google搵資料見到呢條片，就入去睇下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4H_X0Z6kW_E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4H_X0Z6kW_E&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=27309d83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4H_X0Z6kW_E</a><br />\n利申：非打手。唔想幫人加views就直接睇下面，或者自己Google其他片。<br />\n<br />\n根據Wiki：非牛頓流體是一種流體力學的概念，與牛頓流體相對，它的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應力與速度梯度的關係不服從牛頓粘性定律</span></span>，也就是說其剪應力與剪應變呈非線性關係。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即係我地愈大力打佢，佢就愈硬。相反，我地愈細力打佢，佢就好似水咁軟。</span></span><br />\n可以睇上面條片，重點係2分15秒後。<br />\n<br />\n以我所知常見嘅非牛頓流體有：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鷹粟粉、太白粉。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nWiki常見的非牛頓流體包括：<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">高分子聚合物溶液、聚合物熔融體（熔融狀態的塑膠)、泡沫溶液、懸浮液、乳液、膏體(如瀝青)和一些生物流體（如血液）。</span>　呢啲好似太難搵。<br />\n<br />\n唔知對各位學生嘅學術研究有冇用，post咗先算。<br />\n祝各位學業進步。"},{"pid":"e450208bc8b6ec721efa9c8a36e41c4457e457e4","tid":1744510,"uid":203476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T18:45:41.000Z","msg":"post錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadc6f8fa544d6b780d373cd639f9effd6c56a2a","tid":1744510,"uid":167828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T18:47:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9726f52fef802f4ae6a820a4fa171d863a0cc671","tid":1744510,"uid":203476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aadc6f8fa544d6b780d373cd639f9effd6c56a2a","tid":1744510,